## Available Utilities

### Browser Detection

```javascript
import { detectBrowser } from './utils/browserDetection';

const browser = detectBrowser();
console.log(browser.name);      // "Chrome", "Firefox", "Safari", "Edge"
console.log(browser.version);   // 120
console.log(browser.isSupported); // true/false
console.log(browser.isMobile);  // true/false
console.log(browser.isIOS);     // true/false
console.log(browser.isAndroid); // true/false
```

### Feature Detection

```javascript
import { checkFeatureSupport } from './utils/browserDetection';

const features = checkFeatureSupport();
console.log(features.backdropFilter);  // true/false
console.log(features.cssGrid);         // true/false
console.log(features.webSocket);       // true/false
```

### Compatibility Check

```javascript
import { checkCompatibility } from './utils/browserDetection';

const compatibility = checkCompatibility();
console.log(compatibility.isCompatible); // true/false
console.log(compatibility.warnings);     // Array of warnings
console.log(compatibility.recommendations); // Array of recommendations
```

### Performance Recommendations

```javascript
