## Troubleshooting

### Issue: Styles not applying correctly

**Solution:** Clear browser cache and hard reload
```
Chrome/Edge: Ctrl+Shift+R (Windows) or Cmd+Shift+R (Mac)
Firefox: Ctrl+Shift+R (Windows) or Cmd+Shift+R (Mac)
Safari: Cmd+Option+R
```

### Issue: Console errors about unsupported features

**Solution:** Check browser version meets minimum requirements
```javascript
import { detectBrowser, getMinimumVersions } from './utils/browserDetection';

const browser = detectBrowser();
const minimums = getMinimumVersions();
console.log(`Current: ${browser.name} ${browser.version}`);
console.log(`Minimum: ${minimums[browser.name]}`);
```

### Issue: Mobile features not working

**Solution:** Verify device detection
```javascript
import { detectBrowser } from './utils/browserDetection';

const browser = detectBrowser();
console.log('Is Mobile:', browser.isMobile);
console.log('Is iOS:', browser.isIOS);
console.log('Is Android:', browser.isAndroid);
```

### Issue: Performance issues on mobile

**Solution:** Check if performance optimizations are applied
```javascript
import { getPerformanceRecommendations } from './utils/browserDetection';

const recommendations = getPerformanceRecommendations();
console.log('Recommendations:', recommendations);
```

