## Browser-Specific Notes

### Safari
- Requires `-webkit-` prefix for `backdrop-filter`
- Input font-size must be 16px+ to prevent zoom on iOS
- Momentum scrolling requires `-webkit-overflow-scrolling: touch`

### Firefox
- Uses `scrollbar-width` and `scrollbar-color` for scrollbar styling
- Webkit scrollbar properties don't apply

### Chrome/Edge
- Fully supports all modern features
- GPU acceleration works excellently
- Windows High Contrast Mode supported

### Mobile Browsers
- Touch targets must be 44x44px minimum
- Haptic feedback only works on Android
- Safe area insets needed for iPhone X+

