## Performance Targets

All browsers must meet these targets:

- **Load Time:** < 2 seconds ✅
- **Time to Interactive:** < 3 seconds ✅
- **Frame Rate:** 60fps sustained ✅
- **Largest Contentful Paint:** < 2.5s ✅
- **First Input Delay:** < 100ms ✅
- **Cumulative Layout Shift:** < 0.1 ✅

